**How to install the sub packages using composer**
1. Dependency tools
  + Git (sudo apt-get install git)
  + Curl (sudo apt-get install curl)
  + Composer
  	sudo curl -s http://getcomposer.org/installer | php -- --install-dir=path/to/composer/install/dir
2. Using composer to load sub modules/bundles
	sudo php /path/to/composer/install/dir/composer.phar install --dev
	(for more informatiion about using composer: php /path/to/composer/install/dir/composer.phar help)
3. 	
 